{"tid":732512,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個考公開試忍唔住笑既趣事","createTime":"2018-07-07T03:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T08:44:26.000Z","uid":191738,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a47a1ce24bbf8fc9e1df34114420b56eccdb3253","tid":732512,"uid":191738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"早排聽到DSE oral 黃大仙事件，我就諗起自己果年考英文oral 既經歷。<br />\n<br />\n話說當年題目係幫學校攪個遊學團比同學學英文，唔一定要達成共識。咁我英文唔好，當然唔會出聲先。前面既考生都不外乎講美國，歐洲。咁作為屋村仔既我，諗都冇諗過有能力去歐洲啦，同埋覺得個暑假咁短，去咁遠就去得遊就去唔得學，咁我就用呢2個原因話東南亞可能好d. <br />\n<br />\n咁大家就180度轉口風話認同，又開始建議去日本啊，南韓果d. 咁又到我，我又真講果到生活指數都幾高，唔係個個家庭支持到（果時唔係好似依家咁，學生都有能力一年去2次日本。）咁我就話不如去菲律賓，平平地，又大部分人講英文，咁基於時間只餘分半鐘，佢地都只可以焗著認同。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到最後30秒，我講左句：「果實菲律賓人d英文口音唔好，我諗d家長唔會想個仔學呢種口音。」</span><br />\n<br />\n結果2個考官dup低頭狂笑，依其他人用5秒總結話今次傾唔完，下次再傾。<br />\n<br />\n果幾位同學仔，我真心希望果次考你同我一樣合格，我冇心玩你地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ce4e8d88560fd3cb8e87fa119b42c9c800b4a4","tid":732512,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:50:44.000Z","msg":"下次再傾呢下幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d626aa5ae9a26268693434c812d5d5cd0f49691e","tid":732512,"uid":191738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ce4e8d88560fd3cb8e87fa119b42c9c800b4a4","tid":732512,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:50:44.000Z","msg":"下次再傾呢下幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"以前係可以架，老師都係教你唔洗理人，講曬要講既野，唔夠時間就出呢招"},{"pid":"e4ac53daedae02648d4205e31ad1510479f2da2b","tid":732512,"uid":168156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:55:49.000Z","msg":"當年我考個時隔離有條MK妹好型咁攞左火機出黎當塗改液咁放係枱面，問題係連佢自己都冇發現要監考老師同佢講先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我當埸忍唔住笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7c2240cd31c43a9c1fedb3ec28e40a3ae21c78","tid":732512,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:58:25.000Z","msg":"前面條女賴屎"},{"pid":"f1ff24eff7f57fc267552e8a54f556cc286c97c9","tid":732512,"uid":136242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"電台打氣歌播綠柚子，播完即刻再播多次先做到卷，跟住成個腦都係綠柚子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6294f9512b467e56c587e9a29dfd7b340ba669e","tid":732512,"uid":151398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1ff24eff7f57fc267552e8a54f556cc286c97c9","tid":732512,"uid":136242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"電台打氣歌播綠柚子，播完即刻再播多次先做到卷，跟住成個腦都係綠柚子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"綠柚子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9aa7401431be7ef8eb66ba1ffa95fadd6e5523d","tid":732512,"uid":143514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"樓主最尾拎lev 幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8480681f9242d0456af6c8cfed5dffd9d4d65f9a","tid":732512,"uid":191738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9aa7401431be7ef8eb66ba1ffa95fadd6e5523d","tid":732512,"uid":143514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"樓主最尾拎lev 幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 